{"title":"如胶似漆——欢迎范文同总理和其他越南贵宾","authors":["袁鹰"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":6,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"如胶似漆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——欢迎范文同总理和其他越南贵宾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袁鹰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长安街"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘散着巴亭广场的花香；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昆明湖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浮动着还剑湖的碧浪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京蓝色的六月夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎接亲人的好时光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光洒满了大街小巷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如胶似漆的兄弟情到处荡漾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献给你们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数不尽的鲜花耀眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献给你们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱不完的歌声嘹亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有多少情怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要向你们倾诉；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有多少好消息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少件悬念着的事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要请你们讲一讲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请告诉我们："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北方今年雨水顺不顺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稻子长得好不好？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水灾、旱灾、涝灾……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾经使我们一样地心焦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从红河到洞海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从西北平原和北部湾头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又有好多农户，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔上了合作化的大道？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锦普矿的采煤工人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有什么新的发明创造？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滔河两岸无边的甘蔗林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在长得有多高？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南定的姑娘们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"织出了什么新绸布？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越池的钢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高平的锡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海防的水泥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又突破多少指标？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修起几条新公路？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"架成几座新桥？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少孩子戴上红领巾？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少青年跨出高等学校？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一切，这一切啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们全都想知道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竹林边的高脚屋里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老大娘的身体可安好？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常记得那好客的殷勤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说声“中国”就开口笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的侬族母亲啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们收了几吨谷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"买了几幅新年画，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"院子里结了几丛芝麻蕉？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我们又一次欢聚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的心啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀着深情正向南飞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去看同塔梅的莲花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去踩香江的清水；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去探望昆仑岛集中营，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去问候被囚禁在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“稠密区”、“垦荒区”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……的父老兄弟姐妹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请告诉我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们斗争的捷报吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的同志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫叫我们再黯然地紧锁双眉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南方啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炽热的南方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怒火在四处燃烧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁拳指向反动派。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南方啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风暴的南方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美吴集团的罪恶宝座，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝不保夕，摇摇欲坠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请举起杯来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再注满一盏红酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为南方的人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为南方的明天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再干一杯！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京蓝色的六月夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎接亲人的好时光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千朵万朵花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难比美也难比香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千句万句话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诉不尽并肩战友的衷肠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远记住胡主席的话："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越中两个民族，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"素称兄弟之邦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国土接壤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地区毗连，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唇齿相依，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"互为屏障。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"睦南关外春无极，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚滚红河接长江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世世代代好下去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胶漆深情万载长！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1961年6月9日北京"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}